ivardefs.name: active
ivardefs.desc: Whether this organization affiliation record is in active use.

ivardefs.name: code_
ivardefs.desc: Definition of the role the participatingOrganization plays in the association.

ivardefs.name: endpoint_
ivardefs.desc: Technical endpoints providing access to services operated for this role.

ivardefs.name: healthcareService_
ivardefs.desc: Healthcare services provided through the role.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Business identifiers that are specific to this role.

ivardefs.name: location_
ivardefs.desc: The location(s) at which the role occurs.

ivardefs.name: network_
ivardefs.desc: Health insurance provider network in which the participatingOrganization provides the role's services (if defined) at the indicated locations (if defined).

ivardefs.name: organization
ivardefs.desc: Organization where the role is available (primary organization/has members).

ivardefs.name: participatingOrganization
ivardefs.desc: The Participating Organization provides/performs the role(s) defined by the code to the Primary Organization (e.g. providing services or is a member of).

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: The period during which the participatingOrganization is affiliated with the primary organization.

ivardefs.name: specialty_
ivardefs.desc: Specific specialty of the participatingOrganization in the context of the role.

ivardefs.name: telecom_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details at the participatingOrganization relevant to this Affiliation.

properties.desc: Defines an affiliation/assotiation/relationship between 2 distinct oganizations, that is not a part-of relationship/sub-division relationship.
